1. "*Pare* se da ćeš napraviti grešku." (It seems that you are going to make a mistake.) 
2. "*Pare* su se našli da se poprave stvari." (They found the means to fix things.) 
3. "Izgleda da je lako zaraditi *pare*." (It looks like it is easy to earn money.) 
4. "Moraš da razmisliš o tome kako da iskoristiš *pare*." (You have to think about how to make use of the money.) 
5. "On je izgubio *pare* na tržištu." (He lost money on the market.)